 heal and buff IN BETWEEN battles but if they heal during battle, they will take a faction hit. Faction goes down fast, takes about 10 or so kills to go from friendly to KOS. i can never go to felwithe or kelethin again, although i have never been back there since lvl 20. Hope this helps with PoG, and if you see me there, don't bother coming in beacause most of the trash mobs with gems are dead from me farming all day hehe <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . Oh another note, there is no zone out, only ports, gate potions, gate, OT hammer, Gate talismans are only ways to get out. Tell your melees that so they can prepare. Good Luck to you guys. Kill all the butterflies and take a poop in Tunares lake..come on, its fun!<br>
